EXECUTIVE CHEF
05 May 2014 05:14 PM - UAE
Qualifications
* Minimum of 5 years’ experience as an Executive Chef in large
luxury international branded hotels.
* Extensive experience in large conference and events operations.
* Proven leadership of a large kitchen brigade
* Working knowledge of kitchen hygiene practices and occupational
health and safety standards will be essential.
* Computer Skills in MS Office and Outlook as well as working
knowledge of Scala and Hyperion
